txt.en: There are several trolls stationed throughout the White Hand Orc camp. To ensure there isn't an organized attack on Forlaw, the trolls should be defeated.
The trolls stationed throughout the White Hand Orc camp will provide quite a bit of resistance while attempting to collect Orc-heads. Defeat the trolls to make manoeuvring through the camp easier.\n
Defeat trolls throughout the White Hand Orc camp.
Some trolls wander through Fushaum-dorám, likely intended to be a weapon in another White Hand assault. You should defeat the trolls.
You have successfully defeated several of the White Hand trolls at Fushaum-dorám.
Trolls can be found in Fushaum-dorám in the south-eastern Writhendowns.\n\nYou should defeat the trolls.
